unchangedJobs.description:
The E-Commerce Omnichannel Intern has the mission to support the E-commerce Omnichannel Project Manager in all activities related to Omnichannel projects (Ship from Stores, Buy Online Pick up in-store, I-Pad in-store/GStock and, where applicable, Buy Online Return in-store).

CORE JOB RESPONSIBILITIES

## Requirements
- Bachelor's degree;
- Previous working experience in Customer Care or in a store;
- Fluent English. Any additional language is considered a plus;
- Good knowledge of Office package;
- Organizational skills, cooperative and flexible;
- Team working and communication skills;
- Attention to details;
- Think outside the box.

## Benefits
- An International, fresh and dynamic working environment
- Balance between work and personal life: Smart Working (Hybrid work model) and Time flexibility
- Training & Development platform and paths
- Discount on our products both online and in stores

